# Government Tender Announcement
## Cell, Electrocatlyst (Electrochemical Property)
### Reference: cb-5024-45436522

#### Procurement Overview
The Department of National Defence invites proposals to provide electrochemical catalyst cells. The delivery is requested at two locations: Canadian Forces Base (CFB) Halifax, Nova Scotia, and CFB Esquimalt, British Columbia.

#### procurement Details
*   Article 1: GSIN 4630, NSN 01-3209185, Cell, Electrocatlyst 
    *   Part No.: 15MXBCT-02P, NCAGE: 452B2, De Nora Water Technologies Texas LLC
    *   Quantity: 3 Units
    *   Unit of issue: Each 
    *   Delivery Location: CFB Halifax, Nova Scotia
*   Article 2: Same specification as above
    *   Delivery Location: CFB Esquimalt, British Columbia

#### Bidding Information
*   Bidder's shall submit prices in Canadian dollars.
*   Equivalent or substitute products must be independently certified for functionality and caliber, prior to delivery.
*   Each presentation must include a complete product description.
*   Documents may be submitted in either official language of Canada.

#### Legal Considerations
The Crown retains the right to negotiate with suppliers on any procurement.
Lowest Price shall be the evaluating criterion.
 #### Contact Information
 To contact Anthony Lemoine-Hoefsmit, whois the contracting officer at this email address for more information: anthony.lemoine-hoefsmit@forces.gc.ca. You can also reach him by phone at 819-939-3725.

#### Tender Documents
To view the RFQ documentation, please visit the following links:

*   [RFP Attachments English](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/5024/w8482-231237b-english-rfp-clauses.pdf)
*   [RFP Attachments French](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/5024/w8482-231237b-french-rfp-clauses.pdf)
